
moniter_supervisor.sh:
monitor supervisor. should be run on any sueprvisor host. added to crontab with user admin!

moniter_nimbus.sh 
monitor nimbus. should ONLY be run on nimbus host. added to crontab with user admin!

monitor_storm_mem.py
monitor storm worker's memory usage, if > 6G, wangwang alert, if > 10G, killed.
This script is copied to /home/admin/star_storm and add to crontab:
* * * * * /usr/bin/python /home/admin/star_storm/monitor_storm_mem.py

monitor_storm_log.py
monitor storm worker's log, if error level log is found,wangwang alert.
This script is copied to /home/admin/star_storm and add to crontab:
*/5 * * * * /usr/bin/python /home/admin/star_storm/monitor_storm_log.py

